{"ISHMAELITE":[{"def":"A descendant of Ishmael (the son of Abraham and Hagar), of whom it was said, \"His hand will be against every man, and every man's hand against him.","pos":""},{"def":"One at enmity with society; a wanderer; a vagabond; an outcast.","pos":""}],"ISHMAELITISH":[{"def":"Of, pertaining to, or resembling, an Ishmaelite or the Ishmaelites.","pos":""}]}